perl Makefile.PL
make test
make install
./figlet.pl -f standard -d .

This package includes the module, figlet.pl, and the default font standard.flf
a script to emulate the FIGlet command using Text::FIGlet.

NAME
    Text::FIGlet - a perl module to provide FIGlet abilities, akin to banner

SYNOPSIS
     my $font = Text::FIGlet-E<gt>new(-f=>"doh");
     $font->figify(-A=>"Hello World");

#figlet -A Hello World
 _   _      _ _        __        __         _     _ 
| | | | ___| | | ___   \ \      / /__  _ __| | __| |
| |_| |/ _ \ | |/ _ \   \ \ /\ / / _ \| '__| |/ _` |
|  _  |  __/ | | (_) |   \ V  V / (_) | |  | | (_| |
|_| |_|\___|_|_|\___/     \_/\_/ \___/|_|  |_|\__,_|


figlet.pl is still in it's infancy and does not do smushing,
among other things.

#figlet.pl -A Hello World
